defaultEd Coxdefault: This is where we need to look at what a programme of decentralisation looks like, rather than there being one power, to decide to whom something goes, to what level it goes and whether it is appropriate for it to go a level below.  I would look at it over a period of two Parliaments.  If you look at 
defaultJapan
